en: [color bf_yellow]Tuning[/color] - A Rune has a [color bf_green]chance[/color] to improve its Stars and Rarity.\n[color bf_yellow]Failure[/color] - If a Tune fails, it gives a [color bf_green]bonus[/color] to success indicated on the progress bar.\n[color bf_yellow]Max[/color] - Guarantees max Stars and Rarity, and a Passive.
fr: [color bf_yellow]Tuning[/color] - A Rune has a [color bf_green]chance[/color] to improve its Stars and Rarity.\n[color bf_yellow]Failure[/color] - If a Tune fails, it gives a [color bf_green]bonus[/color] to success indicated on the progress bar.\n[color bf_yellow]Max[/color] - Guarantees max Stars and Rarity, and a Passive.
it: [color bf_yellow]Aggiustamento[/color] - Una Runa ha una [color bf_green]chance[/color] di migliorare le sue Stelle e Rarità.\n[color bf_yellow]Fallimento[/color] - Se un Aggiustamento fallisce, aggiunge un [color bf_green]bonus[/color] al successo indicato nella barra dei progressi.\n[color bf_yellow]Max[/color] - Garantisce il massimo di Stelle e Rarità e un Passivo.
de: [color bf_yellow]Tuning[/color] - A Rune has a [color bf_green]chance[/color] to improve its Stars and Rarity.\n[color bf_yellow]Failure[/color] - If a Tune fails, it gives a [color bf_green]bonus[/color] to success indicated on the progress bar.\n[color bf_yellow]Max[/color] - Guarantees max Stars and Rarity, and a Passive.
es: [color bf_yellow]Actualización[/color] - Una Runa tiene la [color bf_green]oportunidad[/color] de mejorar sus Estrellas y Rareza.\n[color bf_yellow]Error[/color] - Si una Afinación falla, le da un [color bf_green]bono[/color] al éxito indicado en la barra de progreso.\n[color bf_yellow]Máximo[/color] - Garantiza el máximo de Estrellas y Rareza, y un Pasivo.

en: Reflects 50% of ranged damage back at the attacker and at the start of each turn will cleanse one debuff on self.

es: Refleja 50% del daño a distancia al atacante y al principio de cada turno limpiará por sí mismo una debilitación.

en:
[color #FFFD29, #FF9D02]Fire VS Water[/color]
Choose a side each day for access
to a [color green]Daily Leaderboard[/color], an [color green]Event
Dungeon[/color], and a [color green]Hero Boost[/color] for
that type of Hero!

Guild Leaderboards are tracked
during the entire Event. Gain
points on the Leaderboards by
completing / quick looting
[color #E78069]Fire[/color] or [color #5AC6F5]Water[/color] dungeons, or by
winning Raids with at least 2
[color #E78069]Fire[/color] or [color #5AC6F5]Water[/color] Heroes on the team!
Choose a side each day and
compete for awesome Rewards!

Sceglie una parte tutti i giorni per accedere
alle [color green]Classifiche del Giorno[/color], un [color green]Sotterraneo
Evento[/color], e un [color green]Potenziamento Eroe[/color] per
quel tipo di Eroe!

Le Classifiche Sodalizio vengono tenute
durante l’intero Evento. Ottieni
punti in Classifica
completando o col saccheggio veloce
di Sotterranei [color #E78069]Fuoco[/color] o [color #5AC6F5]Acqua[/color], o
vincendo Razzie con almeno 2
Eroi [color #E78069]Fuoco[/color] o [color #5AC6F5]Acqua[/color] nel team!
Scegli una parte tutti i giorni e
competi per Ricompense incredibili!

[/color], y una [color green]mejora de héroe[/color] para
ese tipo de héroe!

Las Clasificaciones del Gremio son controladas
durante todo el evento.
¡Gana puntos en las Clasificaciones completando
/ saqueando rápido mazmorras de
[color #E78069]fuego[/color] o [color #5AC6F5]agua[/color], o
ganando saqueos con al menos 2
[color #E78069]Héroes de Fuego[/color] o [color #5AC6F5]Agua[/color] en el equipo!
¡Elige un lado cada día y
compite por premios geniales!
